- Candidate 2 (concise original mixes)
  - Positives vs my tastes: Matches my liking for concise 2–3‑minute singles, warm analogue sonics, tight harmonies, punchy rhythm interplay, dynamic/transient‑preserving mastering and generous headroom — all good. Minimal overdubs and live‑in‑studio immediacy can produce an engaging, honest sound that preserves dynamics.
